,"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Calls to functions in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"vtable"},{"text":" (and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userDataFreeFunc"},{"text":") will happen","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in the thread-default main context"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"(see [method"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GLib.MainContext.push_thread_default"},{"type":"text","text":"])"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"of the thread you are calling this method from.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that all [Variant](\/\/documentation\/glib\/variant values passed to functions in "},{"code":"vtable","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will match"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the signature given in ","type":"text"},{"code":"interfaceInfo","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" - if a remote caller passes"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"incorrect values, the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"org.freedesktop.DBus.Error.InvalidArgs"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is returned to the remote caller."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Additionally, if the remote caller attempts to invoke methods or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"access properties not mentioned in "},{"code":"interfaceInfo","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"org.freedesktop.DBus.Error.UnknownMethod"},{"type":"text","text":" resp."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"org.freedesktop.DBus.Error.InvalidArgs"},{"type":"text","text":" errors"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"are returned to the caller."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is considered a programming error if the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusInterfaceGetPropertyFunc","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" function in ","type":"text"},{"code":"vtable","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" returns a"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"[Variant](\/\/documentation\/glib\/variant of incorrect type.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If an existing callback is already registered at "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"objectPath"},{"type":"text","text":" and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"interface_name"},{"text":", then ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"error"},{"type":"text","text":" is set to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"exists"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"GDBus automatically implements the standard D-Bus interfaces","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"org.freedesktop.DBus.Properties, org.freedesktop.DBus.Introspectable","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and org.freedesktop.Peer, so you don’t have to implement those for the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects you export. You can implement org.freedesktop.DBus.Properties","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"yourself, e.g. to handle getting and setting of properties asynchronously."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Note that the reference count on ","type":"text"},{"code":"interfaceInfo","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"incremented by 1 (unless allocated statically, e.g. if the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"reference count is -1, see "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_dbus_interface_info_ref()"},{"text":") for as long","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"as the object is exported. Also note that "},{"code":"vtable","type":"codeVoice"},{"